{"tid":2512781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度疫情｜ 35歲女患者撲四間醫院無床位車內亡 新德里醫院「缺氧」12病人死","createTime":"2021-05-02T04:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T05:17:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2201d908318f37efd2578d026d84db6a19c4dd23","tid":2512781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:10:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210502/YHXVOCRGUNG4TAC5M7RBLXTYXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210502%2FYHXVOCRGUNG4TAC5M7RBLXTYXU%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=7727e33e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210502%2FYHXVOCRGUNG4TAC5M7RBLXTYXU%2F&h=71a8cb3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210502/YHXVOCRGUNG4TAC5M7RBLXTYXU/</a><br />\n<br />\n印度疫情｜<br />\n35歲女患者撲四間醫院無床位車內亡 新德里醫院「缺氧」12病人死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yzL9TkutuhhxSzL2KuLePyIkJM4=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/W5VSKJ4CDNHZPMXLF3Y2N4QBMQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyzL9TkutuhhxSzL2KuLePyIkJM4%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FW5VSKJ4CDNHZPMXLF3Y2N4QBMQ.jpg&h=45ebc918&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古普塔在車上等入醫院，最終等不到死於車內。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n印度疫情持續惡化，悲劇每天在發生。一名35歲女子上周四被三間醫院拒收，試圖在第四間醫院碰運氣亦失敗，死於醫院停車場車內。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：印度疫情｜為遏疫情疫苗接種對象擴及所有成人 新德里「封城」延長一周<br />\n<br />\n35歲的古普塔（Jagriti Gupta）隻身到新德里南郊諾伊達（Noida）當工程師，與在中央邦生活的丈夫和兩名孩子分隔兩地。她獨住在一個單位，早前確診，上周四病情惡化，一位朋友及包租公嘗試送她入院，不過三間醫院因為床位爆滿而拒收，惟有到政府醫學研究所（GIMS）醫院碰運氣，但結果一樣，在該院停車場等了三小時，最終因為呼吸困難而死於車內。<br />\n<br />\n一位目擊者說，古普塔的包租公四處撲求幫助，但沒有人理會他。古普塔昏倒時，他走進醫院登記處，說古普塔已沒呼吸，醫護趕出去看她，證實她已離世。<br />\n<br />\n悲劇接二連三。新德里的巴特拉醫院周六有12名染疫病人因氧氣短缺而死亡。是不到10天裏新德里發生的第三宗患者缺氧死亡事件。<br />\n<br />\n西部古吉拉特邦（Gujarat）巴羅奇（Bharuch）一幢4層高醫院周六凌晨發生火災，造成18名病人死亡。另外50名病人疏散。<br />\n<br />\n《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n蘋果App大升級 更簡潔更就手！了解更多（立即下載體驗）<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n蘋果初心不變！26周年「撐蘋果Tee」預售：<br />\n<br />\n你的優惠訂購（海外訂購按此）"},{"pid":"10c95c5c44ac65eb5e3bb3b09d7694870065931b","tid":2512781,"uid":382841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"係架車入面等死<br />\n奪命金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c4664ac264ace441d81c71be70ca6418d7c596","tid":2512781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T05:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}